@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = wp.sin((0.56 * wp.abs(v2 + 0.36)))
    v0 = wp.sin(v1)
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v1 + 0.03) / 0.36))
    v0 = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.76 - v2 + 0.03) + v0))
    v0 = wp.cos(v2)
    data[tid] = v0
